          "scid": "thig2.3:1.0.3",
          "en": "3. Sumangala's Mother"
        },
        {
          "scid": "thig2.3:1.0.4",
          "en": "So freed! So freed! So thoroughly freed am I — from my pestle, my shameless husband & his sun-shade making, my moldy old pot with its water-snake smell."
        },
        {
          "scid": "thig2.3:1.0.5",
          "en": "Aversion & passion I cut with a chop. Having come to the foot of a tree, I meditate, absorbed in the bliss: \"What bliss!\""
        }
      ],
